name: Pressure
description: Montenegrin forward Armin Bošnjak of Tampines Rovers FC at a Singapore Premier League match against Lion City Sailors FC on Aug 15, 2021.  This was Tampines Rovers first match in after almost three months and the team was hoping to end their 7-game losing streak in all competitions. However, the team was down 2-0 at half time which made it stressful for the team.
